{
    "title": "SvelteKit App Metrics",
    "uid": "sveltekit-metrics",
    "version": 1,
    "schemaVersion": 39,
    "tags": ["sveltekit"],
    "timezone": "browser",
    "refresh": "10s",
    "time": {
        "from": "now-15m",
        "to": "now"
    },
    "panels": [
        {
            "id": 17,
            "type": "text",
            "title": "",
            "transparent": true,
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 4,
                "w": 24,
                "x": 0,
                "y": 0
            },
            "options": {
                "mode": "markdown",
                "content": "# SvelteKit SSR Skeleton\n\n- **URL:** PLACEHOLDER_URL\n- **GitHub:** https://github.com/stephane-klein/sveltekit-ssr-skeleton\n- **Namespace:** PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 1,
            "title": "Memory",
            "type": "row",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 1,
                "w": 24,
                "x": 0,
                "y": 4
            },
            "description": "M\u00e9triques de m\u00e9moire du processus Node.js (V8)"
        },
        {
            "id": 2,
            "title": "Resident Memory",
            "type": "timeseries",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 6,
                "w": 8,
                "x": 0,
                "y": 5
            },
            "targets": [
                {
                    "expr": "max by(container) (process_resident_memory_bytes{namespace=\"PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE\", app_kubernetes_io_name=\"my-app\"})",
                    "legendFormat": "RSS"
                },
                {
                    "expr": "max by(container) (container_spec_memory_limit_bytes{namespace=\"PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE\",container=\"my-app\"})",
                    "legendFormat": "Memory Limit"
                }
            ],
            "fieldConfig": {
                "defaults": {
                    "unit": "bytes",
                    "decimals": 1,
                    "thresholds": {
                        "mode": "absolute",
                        "steps": [
                            {
                                "color": "green",
                                "value": null
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "orange",
                                "value": 209715200
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "red",
                                "value": 419430400
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    "custom": {
                        "drawStyle": "line",
                        "fillOpacity": 10,
                        "lineWidth": 1,
                        "showPoints": "never"
                    },
                    "min": 0
                },
                "overrides": [
                    {
                        "matcher": {
                            "id": "byName",
                            "options": "Memory Limit"
                        },
                        "properties": [
                            {
                                "id": "custom.fillOpacity",
                                "value": 0
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            "options": {
                "legend": {
                    "displayMode": "list",
                    "placement": "bottom"
                },
                "tooltip": {
                    "mode": "multi"
                }
            },
            "description": "M\u00e9moire r\u00e9sidente (RSS) du processus Node.js \u2014 quantit\u00e9 r\u00e9elle de RAM physique utilis\u00e9e par l'application. Inclut le heap V8, la m\u00e9moire externe (bindings natifs, buffers), le code, la pile d'appels et les librairies charg\u00e9es. Plus fiable que le heap seul pour mesurer l'empreinte m\u00e9moire r\u00e9elle."
        },
        {
            "id": 3,
            "title": "Heap Memory",
            "type": "timeseries",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 6,
                "w": 8,
                "x": 8,
                "y": 5
            },
            "targets": [
                {
                    "expr": "max by(container) (nodejs_heap_size_used_bytes{namespace=\"PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE\", app_kubernetes_io_name=\"my-app\"})",
                    "legendFormat": "Used"
                },
                {
                    "expr": "max by(container) (nodejs_heap_size_total_bytes{namespace=\"PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE\", app_kubernetes_io_name=\"my-app\"})",
                    "legendFormat": "Total"
                }
            ],
            "fieldConfig": {
                "defaults": {
                    "unit": "bytes",
                    "decimals": 1,
                    "custom": {
                        "drawStyle": "line",
                        "fillOpacity": 10,
                        "lineWidth": 1,
                        "showPoints": "never"
                    },
                    "min": 0
                }
            },
            "options": {
                "legend": {
                    "displayMode": "list",
                    "placement": "bottom"
                },
                "tooltip": {
                    "mode": "multi"
                }
            },
            "description": "Used = objets JavaScript allou\u00e9s sur le heap V8 (vivants + en attente de GC). Total = espace r\u00e9serv\u00e9 par V8 (Used + m\u00e9moire inutilis\u00e9e mais pr\u00e9-allou\u00e9e). Le Total augmente par paliers quand V8 agrandit le heap. Surveiller Used pour d\u00e9tecter des fuites m\u00e9moire JS."
        },
        {
            "id": 4,
            "title": "External Memory",
            "type": "timeseries",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 6,
                "w": 8,
                "x": 16,
                "y": 5
            },
            "targets": [
                {
                    "expr": "max by(container) (nodejs_external_memory_bytes{namespace=\"PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE\", app_kubernetes_io_name=\"my-app\"})",
                    "legendFormat": "External"
                }
            ],
            "fieldConfig": {
                "defaults": {
                    "unit": "bytes",
                    "decimals": 1,
                    "thresholds": {
                        "mode": "absolute",
                        "steps": [
                            {
                                "color": "green",
                                "value": null
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "orange",
                                "value": 20971520
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "red",
                                "value": 52428800
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    "custom": {
                        "drawStyle": "line",
                        "fillOpacity": 10,
                        "lineWidth": 1,
                        "showPoints": "never"
                    },
                    "min": 0
                }
            },
            "options": {
                "legend": {
                    "displayMode": "list",
                    "placement": "bottom"
                },
                "tooltip": {
                    "mode": "multi"
                }
            },
            "description": "M\u00e9moire allou\u00e9e en dehors du heap V8 \u2014 buffers Node.js (Buffer.alloc, Buffer.from), bindings natifs C++, libuv, etc. Si cette valeur augmente sans limite, cela peut indiquer une fuite de buffers non lib\u00e9r\u00e9s (ex: streams non consomm\u00e9s, requ\u00eates HTTP non termin\u00e9es)."
        },
        {
            "id": 14,
            "title": "CPU",
            "type": "row",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 1,
                "w": 24,
                "x": 0,
                "y": 11
            },
            "description": "Utilisation CPU du conteneur Node.js"
        },
        {
            "id": 15,
            "title": "CPU Usage",
            "type": "timeseries",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 6,
                "w": 8,
                "x": 0,
                "y": 12
            },
            "targets": [
                {
                    "expr": "max by(container) (rate(process_cpu_seconds_total{namespace=\"PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE\",app_kubernetes_io_name=\"my-app\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
                    "legendFormat": "CPU cores"
                },
                {
                    "expr": "max by(container) (container_spec_cpu_quota{namespace=\"PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE\",container=\"my-app\"}) / ignoring(cpu) max by(container) (container_spec_cpu_period{namespace=\"PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE\",container=\"my-app\"}) * 1000",
                    "legendFormat": "CPU Limit"
                }
            ],
            "fieldConfig": {
                "defaults": {
                    "unit": "millicores",
                    "decimals": 1,
                    "custom": {
                        "drawStyle": "line",
                        "fillOpacity": 10,
                        "lineWidth": 1,
                        "showPoints": "never"
                    },
                    "min": 0
                },
                "overrides": [
                    {
                        "matcher": {
                            "id": "byName",
                            "options": "CPU Limit"
                        },
                        "properties": [
                            {
                                "id": "custom.fillOpacity",
                                "value": 0
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            "options": {
                "legend": {
                    "displayMode": "list",
                    "placement": "bottom"
                },
                "tooltip": {
                    "mode": "multi"
                }
            },
            "description": "Consommation CPU du conteneur en millicores (1 core = 1000 millicores). Correspond aux unit\u00e9s Kubernetes : 100m = 0.1 core, 500m = 0.5 core, 1000m = 1 core. Une app web au repos typiquement < 10 millicores. Une valeur proche de la limite d\u00e9finie dans resources.limits.cpu indique une saturation CPU."
        },
        {
            "id": 16,
            "title": "CPU Usage vs Limit",
            "type": "timeseries",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 6,
                "w": 8,
                "x": 8,
                "y": 12
            },
            "targets": [
                {
                    "expr": "max by(container) (rate(container_cpu_usage_seconds_total{namespace=\"PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE\",container=\"my-app\"}[5m])) / ignoring(cpu) (max by(container) (container_spec_cpu_quota{namespace=\"PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE\",container=\"my-app\"}) / ignoring(cpu) max by(container) (container_spec_cpu_period{namespace=\"PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE\",container=\"my-app\"})) * 100",
                    "legendFormat": "CPU % of limit"
                }
            ],
            "fieldConfig": {
                "defaults": {
                    "unit": "percent",
                    "decimals": 1,
                    "thresholds": {
                        "mode": "absolute",
                        "steps": [
                            {
                                "color": "green",
                                "value": null
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "orange",
                                "value": 80
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "red",
                                "value": 95
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    "custom": {
                        "drawStyle": "line",
                        "fillOpacity": 10,
                        "lineWidth": 1,
                        "showPoints": "never"
                    },
                    "min": 0
                }
            },
            "options": {
                "legend": {
                    "displayMode": "list",
                    "placement": "bottom"
                },
                "tooltip": {
                    "mode": "multi"
                }
            },
            "description": "Pourcentage du quota CPU utilis\u00e9 par le conteneur (bas\u00e9 sur les limites k8s)"
        },
        {
            "id": 5,
            "title": "SQL Queries",
            "type": "row",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 1,
                "w": 24,
                "x": 0,
                "y": 18
            },
            "description": "M\u00e9triques de requ\u00eates SQL PostgreSQL (via pg-promise)"
        },
        {
            "id": 6,
            "title": "SQL Duration p95 / p50",
            "type": "timeseries",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 8,
                "w": 12,
                "x": 0,
                "y": 19
            },
            "targets": [
                {
                    "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by(le, query, container) (rate(sql_query_duration_seconds_bucket{namespace=\"PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE\", app_kubernetes_io_name=\"my-app\"}[5m])))",
                    "legendFormat": "{{query}} p95"
                },
                {
                    "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.5, sum by(le, query, container) (rate(sql_query_duration_seconds_bucket{namespace=\"PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE\", app_kubernetes_io_name=\"my-app\"}[5m])))",
                    "legendFormat": "{{query}} p50"
                }
            ],
            "fieldConfig": {
                "defaults": {
                    "unit": "s",
                    "decimals": 3,
                    "custom": {
                        "drawStyle": "line",
                        "fillOpacity": 10,
                        "lineWidth": 1,
                        "showPoints": "never"
                    },
                    "min": 0
                }
            },
            "options": {
                "legend": {
                    "displayMode": "table",
                    "placement": "right",
                    "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]
                },
                "tooltip": {
                    "mode": "multi"
                }
            },
            "description": "Latence des requ\u00eates SQL \u2014 percentile 95 et m\u00e9dian, par type de requ\u00eate"
        },
        {
            "id": 7,
            "title": "SQL Queries / s",
            "type": "timeseries",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 8,
                "w": 12,
                "x": 12,
                "y": 19
            },
            "targets": [
                {
                    "expr": "sum by(query, container) (rate(sql_query_duration_seconds_count{namespace=\"PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE\", app_kubernetes_io_name=\"my-app\"}[5m]))",
                    "legendFormat": "{{query}}"
                }
            ],
            "fieldConfig": {
                "defaults": {
                    "unit": "cps",
                    "decimals": 1,
                    "custom": {
                        "drawStyle": "line",
                        "fillOpacity": 10,
                        "lineWidth": 1,
                        "showPoints": "never"
                    },
                    "min": 0
                }
            },
            "options": {
                "legend": {
                    "displayMode": "table",
                    "placement": "right",
                    "calcs": ["max"]
                },
                "tooltip": {
                    "mode": "multi"
                }
            },
            "description": "D\u00e9bit de requ\u00eates SQL par seconde, par type de requ\u00eate"
        },
        {
            "id": 8,
            "title": "SSR Render",
            "type": "row",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 1,
                "w": 24,
                "x": 0,
                "y": 27
            },
            "description": "M\u00e9triques de rendu SSR SvelteKit"
        },
        {
            "id": 9,
            "title": "SSR Duration p95 / p50",
            "type": "timeseries",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 8,
                "w": 12,
                "x": 0,
                "y": 28
            },
            "targets": [
                {
                    "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by(le, route, container) (rate(sveltekit_render_duration_seconds_bucket{namespace=\"PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE\", app_kubernetes_io_name=\"my-app\"}[5m])))",
                    "legendFormat": "{{route}} p95"
                },
                {
                    "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.5, sum by(le, route, container) (rate(sveltekit_render_duration_seconds_bucket{namespace=\"PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE\", app_kubernetes_io_name=\"my-app\"}[5m])))",
                    "legendFormat": "{{route}} p50"
                }
            ],
            "fieldConfig": {
                "defaults": {
                    "unit": "s",
                    "decimals": 3,
                    "custom": {
                        "drawStyle": "line",
                        "fillOpacity": 10,
                        "lineWidth": 1,
                        "showPoints": "never"
                    },
                    "min": 0
                }
            },
            "options": {
                "legend": {
                    "displayMode": "table",
                    "placement": "right",
                    "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]
                },
                "tooltip": {
                    "mode": "multi"
                }
            },
            "description": "Temps de rendu SSR \u2014 percentile 95 et m\u00e9dian, par route"
        },
        {
            "id": 10,
            "title": "SSR Renders / s",
            "type": "timeseries",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 8,
                "w": 12,
                "x": 12,
                "y": 28
            },
            "targets": [
                {
                    "expr": "sum by(route, container) (rate(sveltekit_render_duration_seconds_count{namespace=\"PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE\", app_kubernetes_io_name=\"my-app\"}[5m]))",
                    "legendFormat": "{{route}}"
                }
            ],
            "fieldConfig": {
                "defaults": {
                    "unit": "cps",
                    "decimals": 1,
                    "custom": {
                        "drawStyle": "line",
                        "fillOpacity": 10,
                        "lineWidth": 1,
                        "showPoints": "never"
                    },
                    "min": 0
                }
            },
            "options": {
                "legend": {
                    "displayMode": "table",
                    "placement": "right",
                    "calcs": ["max"]
                },
                "tooltip": {
                    "mode": "multi"
                }
            },
            "description": "D\u00e9bit de rendus SSR par seconde, par route"
        },
        {
            "id": 11,
            "title": "Runtime",
            "type": "row",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 1,
                "w": 24,
                "x": 0,
                "y": 36
            },
            "description": "M\u00e9triques d'ex\u00e9cution du runtime Node.js"
        },
        {
            "id": 12,
            "title": "Event Loop Lag",
            "type": "timeseries",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 6,
                "w": 24,
                "x": 0,
                "y": 37
            },
            "targets": [
                {
                    "expr": "max by(container) (nodejs_event_loop_lag_seconds{namespace=\"PLACEHOLDER_NAMESPACE\", app_kubernetes_io_name=\"my-app\"})",
                    "legendFormat": "lag"
                }
            ],
            "fieldConfig": {
                "defaults": {
                    "unit": "s",
                    "decimals": 3,
                    "custom": {
                        "drawStyle": "line",
                        "fillOpacity": 10,
                        "lineWidth": 1,
                        "showPoints": "never"
                    },
                    "min": 0
                }
            },
            "options": {
                "legend": {
                    "displayMode": "list",
                    "placement": "bottom"
                },
                "tooltip": {
                    "mode": "multi"
                }
            },
            "description": "Latence de la boucle d'\u00e9v\u00e9nements Node.js \u2014 doit rester sous 10ms"
        }
    ]
}
